data.description: Come check out this beauty!! Beautiful home with lots of living space. Separate dinging area, with spacious upstairs game room or media room. Home offers an oversized back yard, with room for entertainment.  There's a large split level primary room, with a huge primary restroom offering both a tub and shower, and a large primary closet that offers built in shelving. There's an oversized garage, with a spacious laundry room. Great use of the 2300 sq ft, space.  Seller offering 5k towards closing costs.  Assumable VA loan, option.
